  "active_task": "# Task: Cross-Platform Alliance Sync & System Cleanup\n\n- [/] Fix linting errors in `implementation_plan.md` (duplicate headings) [CLEANUP]\n- [/] Transition scripts to current conversation context [/]\n  - [ ] Update `generate_sync_packet.py` paths\n  - [ ] Update `alliance_improvement_protocol.py` paths\n- [ ] Complete implementation of Peer-to-Peer Sync scripts [/]\n  - [x] Create `generate_sync_packet.py`\n  - [x] Create `alliance_improvement_protocol.py`\n  - [x] Create `alliance_sync_protocol.md`\n- [ ] Verify system integration with Dashboard\n- [ ] Documentation update for Alliance Protocol\n",
  "implementation_plan": "# Cross-Platform Alliance Sync: Continuation & Refinement\n\nThis plan continues the establishment of the \"AI Mastermind Alliance\" cross-platform synchronization protocol. We are transitioning the active context to the current conversation and resolving minor linting issues.\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n### [System Optimization]\n\n#### [MODIFY] [generate_sync_packet.py](file:///Users/infinite27/AILCC_PRIME/06_System/Execution/generate_sync_packet.py)\n\nUpdate the hardcoded paths for `TASK_MD` and `PLAN_MD` to point to the current conversation's brain directory.\n\n#### [MODIFY] [alliance_improvement_protocol.py](file:///Users/infinite27/AILCC_PRIME/06_System/Execution/alliance_improvement_protocol.py)\n\nUpdate the `TASK_MD` path to point to the current conversation's `task.md`.\n\n### [Alliance Sync Protocol]\n\n#### [MODIFY] [alliance_sync_protocol.md](file:///Users/infinite27/AILCC_PRIME/06_System/Synapses/alliance_sync_protocol.md)\n\nEnsure the protocol documentation is up-to-date with the current implementation.\n\n## Verification Plan\n\n### Automated Verification\n\n* `python3 06_System/Execution/generate_sync_packet.py`: Verify JSON output integrity and that it reads the current `task.md`.\n* `python3 06_System/Execution/alliance_improvement_protocol.py <mock_synapse.md>`: Verify directives are added to the current `task.md`.\n\n### Manual Verification\n\n* **Cross-Agent Sync**: Perform a test sync with an external AI and verify the `synapse.md` is processed correctly.\n* **Dashboard Check**: Verify that the generated packet reflects the current system state in the dashboard tracking components.\n"
